{"tid":768250,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[多圖]動物台五毛會員大起底","createTime":"2018-08-05T08:21:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-05T09:58:38.000Z","uid":34293,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"a88d1b9090f6deedd3781433c59b6b84b0756f5b","tid":768250,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T08:21:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪有人會好奇,究竟呢班經常圍威喂既動物台會員,究竟真人係咩樣呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n以下呢堆相,係同過佢地踢波/入group賭錢而得到佢資料,再起底得返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n首先打頭陣既有<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五毛群龍共舞</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/07/11/143047_ae208d9c54dc2f756a09e69b82c8f084.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F07%2F11%2F143047_ae208d9c54dc2f756a09e69b82c8f084.jpg&h=ce2b766a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/07/11/143400_da484a208cc929e2d56bd3a615a48fda.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F07%2F11%2F143400_da484a208cc929e2d56bd3a615a48fda.jpg&h=d6498b36&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">蛇頭:水樹奈奈</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20120713/large/13ls7p106n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20120713%2Flarge%2F13ls7p106n.jpg&h=02e9882a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">蛇仔:天才小釣手</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/07/11/142159_5dfb7447164de6ab2116b84361884351.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F07%2F11%2F142159_5dfb7447164de6ab2116b84361884351.jpg&h=801ff19f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">藍屍:巴麻美(左)19仔(右)</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.epochtimes.com/assets/uploads/2013/07/1307281255501991-600x399.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.epochtimes.com%2Fassets%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F07%2F1307281255501991-600x399.jpg&h=5ada5050&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">龍三(塩川洋介弟子)</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://lh5.ggpht.com/_wvMTJbMBEXw/SiP15HgpuII/AAAAAAAAI48/xP2YoPxgz2k/s400/IMG_0702-1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flh5.ggpht.com%2F_wvMTJbMBEXw%2FSiP15HgpuII%2FAAAAAAAAI48%2FxP2YoPxgz2k%2Fs400%2FIMG_0702-1024.jpg&h=dae0a5a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">精神病會員喪心病狂</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/07/11/160219_080c2e2b4fb48218e16e65d107d2183f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F07%2F11%2F160219_080c2e2b4fb48218e16e65d107d2183f.jpg&h=b5f52ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/07/11/160340_53be41363a3eec40995e1b9f2ba10192.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F07%2F11%2F160340_53be41363a3eec40995e1b9f2ba10192.jpg&h=0bb07cf5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">明眼人</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/07/11/143851_85859d0e34d5e897758579165e01c2ec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F07%2F11%2F143851_85859d0e34d5e897758579165e01c2ec.jpg&h=5f88de73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ese